lead_paragraph: Reserve Ja'Quan Newton scored 18 points and No. 15 Miami overcame a flurry of misses in the paint to beat Wake Forest 77-63 on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Newton's 18 Helps No. 15 Miami Beat Wake Forest 77-63
